svg.title: Trillion Fund
svg.desc: rillion is an FCA-regulated peer-to-project platform allowing everyone to invest in UK clean energy. In 2014, we raised £1.6 million for renewable energy projects. In 2015, we’re planning on raising a further £10 million. There is £1 trillion sitting in UK banks earning less than the rate of inflation, and losing money in real terms. £1 trillion a year is also the amount needed to fund sufficient renewable energy to stay within two degrees of warming.
